data.description: Beautiful two story home in developing Altoona! Walking into the main floors open floorplan. Kitchen includes SS appliances granite counters, and ample storage. Enjoy the fireplace and covered deck ready for entertainment. Upstairs you will find 2 bedrooms, full bath, and a Primary ensuite. The finished walk out basement offers a 4th bedroom, 3/4 bath, and family room. Summers can be spent enjoying your pool & fenced yard. Shed is heated and cooled for your shop projects!
